Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.40,0:00:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人偶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.93,0:00:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么愿望\N都能帮你实现喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.83,0:00:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的愿望都可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.97,0:00:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 只能许三个喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的什么样的愿望都可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 因为实现愿望的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我做不到的不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我的第一个愿望是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间的黄昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.62,0:01:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行着一段永远的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.67,0:01:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖继续探索着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.74,0:01:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片发出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.08,0:01:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.26,0:01:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找遗失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.19,0:01:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手的掌心确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.93,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.27,0:01:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间开始流动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.15,0:02:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「约定」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了 天亮了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点吃完早饭 到学校去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天放假 你起得还真早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.07,0:02:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为名雪闹钟的威力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 又下雪了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常安静呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.03,0:02:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 佑一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在商店街抽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影票…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车站前的电影院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像到今天为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得抽到\N不用的话就太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就找名雪一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.71,0:03:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪因为要帮忙社团\N到隔壁镇上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在等人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要等你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛否定得那么直接嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我怎么否定啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太清楚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影票 秋子阿姨给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要跟谁去呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.16,0:03:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有兴趣吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟佑一去看电影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那去看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.11,0:04:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用害怕的那么夸张吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难得来看电影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少也该体会一下\N现场的气氛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在体会了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么…\N还我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次的比赛也要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.98,0:04:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起看电影 看亚由还更有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好坏心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一变得有精神了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才的佑一\N看起来很寂寞的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.67,0:05:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在这 好像一个人等待着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不会来的某人的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是笑的时候比较适合佑一喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.65,0:05:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我以前跟亚由你\N说过的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个模仿别人说话的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要吃些什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 吃什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃点能填饱的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我想要早点回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.71,0:05:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么要紧的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得这张长椅吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.29,0:06:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我跟佑一常常约在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.06,0:06:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对以前…七年前的事情\N几乎都不记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.00,0:06:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.11,0:06:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要再次来到这个城市\N也是不知为何的很抗拒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.91,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然来到这个城市的时间不长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却发生了很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有快乐的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也有很悲伤的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.29,0:06:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不来到这个城市的话\N就不会遇到这种…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.89,0:06:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴能跟佑一\N在这个城镇再次相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直坐在这张长椅上\N等着佑一到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直…一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.81,0:06:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直等着你\N所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是要跟我们一起去吃东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.44,0:07:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没顾虑到佑一的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.71,0:07:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 说这种话\N我也会害羞的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有「但是」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是用跑的回来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有点晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上做晚饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 你回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.07,0:08:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧在车站前遇到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好正在做晚餐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由愿意的话\N要不要一起来吃呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.05,0:08:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便\N要不要顺便住下来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡衣向名雪借就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.37,0:09:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我刚才已经吃过了\N所以不吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你房间还亮着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件睡衣是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不太适合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我小了一点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也没错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.74,0:09:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有些话想对你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会打扰到你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经洗过澡了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还戴着发箍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前说过的事你还记得吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个很重要的人\N送给我的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 我好像记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 你还记得那天的事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.81,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.87,0:10:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一\N把发箍送给我当礼物的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.48,0:10:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一你就是那个对我最重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不记得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.56,0:10:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过了七年了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算佑一你忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.77,0:10:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你送给我的发箍\N现在还是在这里喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.67,0:10:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且佑一现在\N不是就在我面前吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 这是向你道谢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.36,0:11:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经…不适合我…了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 晚安 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 那个发箍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的第一个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要忘了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寒假结束之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.57,0:11:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使回到了自己的城镇去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.97,0:11:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也好\N请想起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「在下着雪的城市\N遇到过一个奇怪的女孩」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样也好 也请不要忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的第一个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.76,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有社团活动\N不早点去不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要看这个节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本周的占卜时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.40,0:12:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本周的山羊座 运气有点糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一切看来平稳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去 名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.95,0:12:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？名雪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占卜说我…运气很不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太在意喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.66,0:12:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有从很久以前\N就跟亚由见过面的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:12:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一你早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你起的真早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.21,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有社团活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.95,0:13:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.79,0:13:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道七年前的冬天\N在这小镇上发生的事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然问这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实没什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 早安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.77,0:13:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就准备佑一跟亚由的早饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微客气一点好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.68,0:13:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.92,0:13:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 这么冷真是不想去学校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的学校休息喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.99,0:13:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.76,0:13:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不去的时候就可以不去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种学校吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是连亚由都能上的学校嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过份喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最喜欢的学校呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑 开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.87,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 从以前我就想问了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.34,0:14:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个背包里面到底装些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,装什么？很普通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教科书啊笔记啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.02,0:14:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有些向朋友借的CD\N杂志等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很普通嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我已经那样说了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有歪掉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你在这里没关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走过头了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真像笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.41,0:14:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是佑一你恶作剧的关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.94,0:14:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啦 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.19,0:14:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后再一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那个长椅上见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.26,0:14:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去商店街吃鲷鱼烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去打电动 还有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.06,0:15:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去亚由喜欢的学校看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来\N你在找的东西找到了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.05,0:15:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.01,0:15:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也许找不到才好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为能跟佑一见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.72,0:15:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟佑一说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.46,0:15:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能像这样跟佑一在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.63,0:15:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我来说是最幸福的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.24,0:15:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然很幸福\N为什么露出这样的表情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我变得软弱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.54,0:15:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很害怕这种幸福…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕眼前的现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定其实只是某人\N正在做的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.48,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.92,0:16:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一曾经失去过很重要的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.23,0:16:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我除了哭泣之外什么都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能哭着呼喊那个人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里都不会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天结束春天来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使雪溶化了\N我也会一直在这个城镇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远在亚由你的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 你握的那么紧我会痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里都不会去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我胸部可能很小喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.49,0:16:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个胆小鬼\N也不会做料理喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.43,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使会后悔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.18,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我也不会后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.15,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为佑一的身体 好温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.58,0:17:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜欢佑一喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的东西\N一定是变得幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像来到一个\N不得了的地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪会啊 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我的学校喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 这里只有一棵被砍掉的树吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.57,0:17:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在上的学校…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明今天也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里真的是我的学校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.12,0:18:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天都是我一直在上\N最喜欢的学校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还在这里拿到发箍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在这里佑一你送我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你想不起来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.26,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 那是骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.41,0:18:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里…我记得…我知道这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.31,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.09,0:18:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不找到的话…不找到的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 亚由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不该存在的人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的第二个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.21,0:19:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟佑一去同一个学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟他一起去学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起读书\N一起吃午餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.82,0:19:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起打扫\N还有跟佑一一起回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有…没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N手都受伤了不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约定喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.93,0:19:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 为什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 你到底怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 其实什么都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是\N想起了以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有…这？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.89,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是已经知道了\N在找的东西是什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.49,0:20:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是埋在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天再来找吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会帮你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.04,0:20:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许夜晚已经不会再过去了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易再会了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.92,0:20:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…\N好不容易感情变好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想我们\N不会再见面了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.54,0:20:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 你在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.34,0:20:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.08,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做着悠久而遥远的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相同的日子不停重复着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.22,0:21:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在永不终结的梦里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期盼着…不可能来到的早晨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.43,0:21:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 又回到了同样的梦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.27,0:21:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲜红的、洁白的、冰冷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.84,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温暖的、悲伤的、高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.51,0:21:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.41,0:21:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 同样的日子\N继续不断的转动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.75,0:21:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在很久之前…\N好多年前就已经就注意到了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.45,0:21:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在永不结束的梦里漂流着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待着…不可能降临的黎明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一样的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声音忽然地消逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.36,0:21:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记不起容貌的人在出现眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.77,0:21:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个没有人会去注意到的\N孤单的小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等着人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着明知不会出现的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.74,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道不会再见面的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论经过多少年 多少岁月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不停轮回的梦中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.62,0:22:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直等着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.99,0:22:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能来临的…黎明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.27,0:22:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从随风飘流的云朵之间\N窥视到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.22,0:22:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连熟悉的街道也闪闪发光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.39,0:22:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.80,0:22:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.70,0:23:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真来盖过溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.28,0:23:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间静悄悄的流动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.26,0:23:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂着温柔的风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.86,0:23:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为冻僵的思念也会化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.08,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.91,0:23:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪带给心乱如麻的我力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.12,0:23:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能响应这样的爱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.59,0:23:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第12话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦的痕迹
